Description: Killing me to sell my girl but I must. Got her back in 2014 and really never got to play her. Shes been on the stand, in the bag or on my wall stand most of the time as you can see by her condition. Rarely played and never gigged with. Never left this house actually. Stock humbucker was replaced with a seymour Duncan but Im not sure what model. I had a tech friend do that a long time ago and I dont have any documents on it. She comes with a stand, strap and gig bag. She could probably use a set up and if I remember the high E was a little twangy. Nothing horrible or deal breaking at all, I just like to disclose all I know about my items. Thanks for looking and let me know if you have any questions! Take good care of her.
